reviews.review_text: No new ground but a great show We we're all so happy to be there again, throughout all of these shows.  I was lucky to make it to all 4(mail order and got a Christmas card from the Dead that year, too!).  Garcia's voice was rejuvenated and the musical exploration was starting anew;  sometimes like baby steps and then gaining confidence.  The Hamza El-Din, Nevilles support team helped to push this show into one of the greats. Haven't heard this for a while, but I like this recording, so far better than the rest of the audience recordings.

Very nice This is a good sounding tape. I love the aud's. considering they had the OTS at this point you did a fine job. Loved these shows. I consider myself very lucky to have been on tour during the early to late 80'2 Raw garage band style dead.
 If anyone is considering this version for downloading do it.....
